<item>
            <title>[LU-16076] add argument to specify file system for command &apos;lfs check&apos;</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16076</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Add an optional argument for &lt;tt&gt;lfs check&lt;/tt&gt; command to specify lustre file system to be checked.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;As a reference, &lt;tt&gt;lfs osts&lt;/tt&gt; shows all the OSTs for all mounted lustre file system, and &lt;tt&gt;lfs ost /mnt/lustre&lt;/tt&gt; shows only the OSTs of /mnt/lustre.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So will enhance command &lt;tt&gt;lfs check servers /mnt/lustre&lt;/tt&gt; to show only the servers of /mnt/lustre. &lt;tt&gt;lfs check servers&lt;/tt&gt; shows all the servers of mounted lustre file system as before.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
